TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: 08/28/2014 - BSR 10094 (RCI Batch Defects): This tranformation will look up VRAP.RCIT_CLM_BTCH_CNTL table and return the Batch gid if the batch was in balanced state (BTCH_STAT_CD=20) in the past 4 days.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_BTCH_GID_In_Balanace

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT A.BTCH_GID as BTCH_GID_Balance FROM VRAP.RCIT_CLM_BTCH_CNTL A WHERE A.BTCH_STAT_CD=20 AND A.BTCH_STAT_TS > CURRENT TIMESTAMP - 4 DAYS

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: 08/28/2014 - BSR 10094 (RCI Batch Defects): This acts as a passthrough transformation and will convert BTCH_GID to integer format so it can be used to look up VRAP.RCIT_CLM_BTCH_CNTL.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: EXP_BTCH_GID

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: 08/28/2014 - BSR 10094 (RCI Batch Defects): This transformation will filter out all batches which are not in balanced state and will load only those batches which are in Balanced State (VRAP.RCIT_CLM_BTCH_CNTL.BTCH_STAT_CD=20)
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: FIL_BTCH_OOB
